on trunk r18368, this delightful little poison pill:
{code}
(Nil:List[List[Double]]).reduceLeft((_: Any, _: Any) => Nil.indices.map(_ => 0d))
{code}

sends the compiler into an apparently infinite loop.  a sample thread dump shows:
